body: "CONTEXT: scripts/CI need to branch on failure category without parsing stderr. DECISION: EXIT_CODE in src/core/shared/constants.ts is the single source of truth and is stable: 2 usage, 3 not_found, 4 conflict (lock/ownership), 5 dependency_failed (preflight), 1 generic; telemetry maps these to taxonomy/resolution codes. CONSEQUENCES: deterministic scripting; every new PmCliError must map to an existing code; adding a new code is a breaking change for callers. EVIDENCE: src/core/shared/constants.ts EXIT_CODE; src/cli/main.ts classification."
